  },
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Clinical Setting"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "items": [
        "The most common form of anthrax infection, usually naturally acquired but may be acquired from a bioterrorism event.",
        "History of exposure to hides, hair or wool with introduction of spores into non-intact skin.",
        "Painless enlarging papule on exposed skin of face, neck, arms or hands. Lesions enlarge with central painless ulcer covered by black eschar and edema of surrounding tissue. Lymphadenitis and regional adenopathy can occur."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Diagnosis"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Gram stain and culture or PCR."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Etiologies"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "items": [
        "Bacillus anthracis"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Primary Regimens"
    },
    {
      "type": "nestedContent",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Empiric therapy of cutaneous anthrax and no evidence of systemic disease based on 2023 CDC guidelines."
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "If systemic symptoms, treat for more severe disease."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Duration of therapy: 7 to 10 days unless an aerosol exposure may have occurred in which case transition to a post-exposure prophylaxis regimen to complete 60 days of treatment."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "drugRegimen",
      "regimenData": {
        "intent": "treatment",
        "appliesTo": {
          "description": "Nonpregnant adults age > 18 yrs"
        },
        "components": [
          {
            "drug": "Ciprofloxacin",
            "dose": "500 mg",
            "route": "po",
            "frequency": "q12h",
            "connector": "or"
          },
          {
            "drug": "Doxycycline",
            "dose": "100 mg",
            "route": "po",
            "frequency": "q12h"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
